# Notes
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# RPC Provider Comparison:
#
# Alchemy
# - Pros: Generous free tier, good docs, reliable
# - Cons: Archive nodes expensive
#
# Infura
# - Pros: Established provider, simple pricing
# - Cons: Rate limits on free tier
#
# QuickNode
# - Pros: Archive access, good performance
# - Cons: Higher cost
#
# Public RPCs (not recommended)
# - Pros: Free
# - Cons: Unreliable, rate limited, no archive access

# Archive Node Requirements:
# - Module 1 (Event Filters): Regular node OK
# - Module 2 (Simulation): Archive node REQUIRED
# - Module 3 (Indexing): Not needed (services handle it)

# Security:
# - Never commit your .env file
# - Don't share API keys
# - Use read-only keys when possible
# - Rotate keys regularly
